name: Creation of Eve
description: Soaring in the air of heaven, floating through the battlefields to protect her innocence, so different from the others. Inside she is surrounded with beauty and happiness. As time passed, she became more powerful and stronger but as she grew more evil people began to quarrel about who was better; man or woman. This created a deep-rooted hatred that could never be repaired by any means and it eventually led to her fall from grace.
